frame0.consensus_text: We have an account that severall persons of good consideration are taken up
in the Bishoprick of Durham upon the account of false Coyning - Yesterday
morning a Lusty young fellow 6 foot high who was taken for a Recruit &
put into the Compter hamstring'd himself by cutting one of his Leggs into
the Bone to prevent his going a Soldier by which he'l loose his Limb
if not his life. - P.S. Paris 25. Mon<sw-sup>r</sw-sup> Peticun is upon his return -
for Holland the Court being not enclined to embrace the propositions for Peace
